summary: Hello nexus people. I am Karbinder, and i proudly present my first mod to skyrim. I spent alot of work on this and hoped you would enjoy this challenge. I created a area that is meant for high leveled players. It is located near the shearpoint on a mountain north-west to Riften. It is a very simple mod so don't expect much.
